      "rationale": "Formal model input uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2. Nominal input values sourced from published literature and manufacturer specifications. Sensitivity to key inputs (viscosity, hematocrit) qualitatively assessed and found to have minor influence on relative hemolysis ranking."
